<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ yào zhī dào yáng xū yào mù rén, mù rén gèng xū yào yáng qún.
 shí dài xū yào fú yīn nǎ, hé chǎng xū yào gōng rén. shì jiè gè guó dōu shì yī tiáo gēn.
 bù guǎn shì kù shǔ hái shì fēng xuě yè guī rén dōu yǒu dì xiōng xīn qín kǔ bēn.
 ná shén me jiàn fù shén. mén xīn zì wèn, wù yào jǐn nǐ lǐng shòu de zhí fèn.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ yào zhī dào yáng xū yào mù rén 迦南484</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>484</hymn_number>
</song>